record_data.record_plain_text: CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE This is to certify that Wildflower Solar 3 LLC assents to and concurs in the Shared Facilities and Co-Tenancy Agreement, which the designated filing company, Wildflower Solar LLC, has filed. Wildflower Solar 3 LLC hereby files this Certificate of Concurrence in lieu of filing the rate schedule specified.
